io.github.kkysen.quicktrip.apis

Annotation Type QueryField


  • @Documented
 @Retention(value=RUNTIME)
 @Target(value=FIELD)
public @interface QueryField
    signifies that a field is a @QueryField will be found through reflection and added to the CachedApiRequest.QueryParams in CachedApiRequest if include() = false, then it will not be automatically added and must be done in CachedApiRequest.modifyQuery(QueryParams)
    Author:
    Khyber Sen
    See Also:
    CachedApiRequest.modifyQuery(QueryParams), CachedApiRequest.reflectQuery()
